Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Airplane
    This class represents an airplane with an (x,y) coordinate and velocities in the x and y direction
    Background
    Represents a background for the plane, containing scenery images and fires
    Cockpit
    This class represents the cockpit of an airplane with altitude measurement and dial for speed
    Dial
    This class represents a dial that keeps track of a measurement, specifically speed
    Fire
    This class represents an animated fire with (x,y) coordinate and can either be extinguished/not extinguished
    FlightSimulation
    This class represents a flight simulation (2d side view), containing the Airplane and Background objects.
    Image
    This class represents an Image with (x,y) coordinate
    InstructionsPanel
    This class represents the Instructions Panel, which allows user to seek help and select airport options
    LocationTracker
    Represents a LocationTracker which tracks the plane's flight
    Main
    This class contains the Main method and implements the Fire Flighter Game
    PilotPanel
    This class represents the pilot's view of the flight simulation and extends PApplet
    Runway
    This class represents a runway with an (x,y) coordinate
    WaterSpray
    This class represents a single spray of water, which the plane can shoot at the fires
